name: Fall Dimensional
description:
FALL DIMENSIONAL

Jump from dimension to dimension. Try to time your timing well, solve levels in a short time to get stars and be careful not to fall ;)

  • Finish levels within the time limit
  • 14 levels
  • Menu options to change the movements

Controls:

  • WASD: Simple FPS movement
  • SPACE: Jump
  • E: Change dimension
  • ESC: Pause

CREDITS:
